510
00:30:45,240 --> 00:30:46,340
You'll find out when you get there.

511
00:30:47,020 --> 00:30:47,920
We'll set out tomorrow.

512
00:30:48,300 --> 00:30:49,310
Where are we going?

513
00:30:49,410 --> 00:30:50,430
Just come with me.

514
00:30:50,780 --> 00:30:51,840
