to the mountains.

535
00:31:45,500 --> 00:31:47,080
But I can't just sit here and wait.

536
00:31:47,840 --> 00:31:49,000
Mr Wu, don't worry.

537
00:31:49,180 --> 00:31:50,020
At this moment,

538
00:31:50,100 --> 00:31:51,880
