I'm not interested in your story,

563
00:33:26,650 --> 00:33:27,600
just cut to the chase.

564
00:33:30,060 --> 00:33:31,730
Young people like you

565
00:33:31,870 --> 00:33:33,160
are too short-tempered,

566
00:33:33,340 --> 00:33:34,520
you're impatient.

567
00:33:35,250 --> 00:33:37,280
I found an important clue

568
00:33:38,100 --> 00:33:39,890
which is closely related

569
00:33:40,640 --> 00:33:41,620
to the Yellow Silk you're looking for.

570
00:33:41,810 --> 00:33:42,710
Just tell us

571
00:33:42,810 --> 00:33:44,030
what exactly it is.

572
00:33:44,540 --> 00:33:47,000
That clue is actually a place.

573
00:33:48,170 --> 00:33:49,070
Here is it.

574
00:33:49,450 --> 00:33:50,390
You know what,

575
00:33:50,860 --> 00:33:52,880
don't ever underestimate this field.

576
00:33:53,800 --> 00:33:54,700
Back then, Master Buddha

577
00:33:54,780 --> 00:33:57,120
found it after a lot of hard work.

578
00:33:57,690 --> 00:34:00,540
Besides, a big secret actually lies here.

579
00:34:01,380 --> 00:34:02,280
Stop the cart!

580
00:34:02,660 --> 00:34:04,260
Don't stop! We're not there yet.

581
00:34:04,480 --> 00:34:05,970
Sirs, who should I listen to?

582
00:34:06,050 --> 00:34:07,440
Listen to me. Stop the cart!

583
00:34:09,560 --> 00:34:10,530
Enough is enough.

584
00:34:10,610 --> 00:34:11,510
Stop acting already.

585
00:34:11,810 --> 00:34:13,110
Master Buddha would never come here.

586
00:34:13,560 --> 00:34:14,610
Even if he had,

587
00:34:14,740 --> 00:34:16,120
he left empty-handed.

588
00:34:16,290 --> 00:34:17,170
Even if Master Buddha left empty-handed

589
00:34:17,250 --> 00:34:18,960
it doesn't mean
that we'll end up the same way.

590
00:34:19,040 --> 00:34:19,940
Mop,

591
00:34:20,250 --> 00:34:21,710
keep driving. It's right ahead of us.

592
00:34:22,520 --> 00:34:23,420
Sirs,

593
00:34:23,610 --> 00:34:24,710
who should I listen to?

594
00:34:24,920 --> 00:34:25,820
Listen to me!

595
00:34:27,300 --> 00:34:28,120
Shoot.

596
00:34:28,200 --> 00:34:29,100
Who exactly hired you?

597
00:34:29,760 --> 00:34:31,150
No one hired me.

598
00:34:31,610 --> 00:34:33,290
I just want to share with you

599
00:34:33,370 --> 00:34:34,780
the important clue which I found.

600
00:34:35,600 --> 00:34:36,990
Would you be so kind?

601
00:34:37,240 --> 00:34:38,230
Take out the credit card machine.

602
00:34:39,610 --> 00:34:40,710
You want to pay me?

603
00:34:49,820 --> 00:34:51,050
A good guy like me

604
00:34:51,260 --> 00:34:52,530
conducts business based on trust.

605
00:34:52,710 --> 00:34:55,050
I will never disclose
any of my clients' information.

606
00:34:56,150 --> 00:34:57,050
It's Master Er.

607
00:34:57,190 --> 00:34:58,090
Master Er from the Wu family.

608
00:34:58,950 --> 00:35:00,080
What did he ask you to do?

609
00:35:01,150 --> 00:35:02,120
No signal?

610
00:35:02,490 --> 00:35:03,390
No,

611
00:35:03,480 --> 00:35:04,860
how is this possible?

612
00:35:07,970 --> 00:35:08,920
No signal?

613
00:35:10,820 --> 00:35:11,720
No signal.

614
00:35:14,010 --> 00:35:16,280
How could there be no signal
at this critical moment?

615
00:35:16,360 --> 00:35:17,260
Mr Black,

616
00:35:17,490 --> 00:35:18,650
you know you can trust

617
00:35:18,730 --> 00:35:20,110
Xiao Hua.

618
00:35:20,690 --> 00:35:22,920
I will be the guarantor of the fees.

619
00:35:23,720 --> 00:35:25,620
He will pay you a handsome sum.

620
00:35:26,380 --> 00:35:28,540
Why did Master Er hire you?

621
00:35:34,220 --> 00:35:35,800
As a matter of fact, it was nothing.

622
00:35:36,420 --> 00:35:37,480
He wanted me

623
00:35:37,560 --> 00:35:38,860
to take you guys around.

624
00:35:39,420 --> 00:35:40,320
Take a walk

625
00:35:40,490 --> 00:35:41,390
and relax.

626
00:35:41,880 --> 00:35:43,520
Go somewhere irrelevant,

627
00:35:44,380 --> 00:35:45,700
as long as you don't wander off.

628
00:35:46,800 --> 00:35:47,850
Where does he not want me to go?

629
00:35:48,420 --> 00:35:49,560
It depends

630
00:35:51,040 --> 00:35:53,470
on where you're going.

631
00:36:09,190 --> 00:36:10,090
Sir,

632
00:36:10,190 --> 00:36:11,530
can you take Wu Xie into the mountain?

633
00:36:15,310 --> 00:36:16,210
No.

634
00:36:17,300 --> 00:36:18,380
Mr Panma,

635
00:36:18,630 --> 00:36:19,980
back in Buffalo Trench,

636
00:36:20,060 --> 00:36:22,540
-I...
-Since we managed to get out of it,

637
00:36:23,060 --> 00:36:25,950
I guess we're considered sworn friends.

638
00:36:27,850 --> 00:36:29,510
Of course I'm willing to help you.

639
00:36:31,470 --> 00:36:33,570
But with the current situation,

640
00:36:34,150 --> 00:36:35,050
I really can't do it.

641
00:36:35,950 --> 00:36:37,340
When I got here, I heard

642
00:36:37,420 --> 00:36:38,490
that it had been raining for two days.

643
00:36:38,630 --> 00:36:39,550
But look.

644
00:36:39,630 --> 00:36:40,600
The rain has stopped.

645
00:36:40,680 --> 00:36:42,460
The rain has stopped here.

646
00:36:43,250 --> 00:36:44,200
But it might not be the same

647
00:36:44,310 --> 00:36:45,240
in the mountain.

648
00:36:46,110 --> 00:36:47,730
It's very cloudy in the mountain,

649
00:36:48,150 --> 00:36:49,840
there must be a heavy downpour.

650
00:36:50,420 --> 00:36:52,690
Maybe there's a mudslide now.

651
00:36:53,390 --> 00:36:54,840
Mr Gui was right.

652
00:36:56,310 --> 00:36:57,930
Whoever goes into the mountains now

653
00:36:58,270 --> 00:36:59,550
will die on his way there.

654
00:36:59,630 --> 00:37:02,280
-But...
-My dad lacks experience.

655
00:37:02,360 --> 00:37:04,070
He only goes to the mountain
a few times a year.

656
00:37:04,150 --> 00:37:06,460
But you go there everyday,
there won't be any problems.

657
00:37:06,630 --> 00:37:10,520
Yun Cai, you grew up in the mountains,

658
00:37:11,150 --> 00:37:13,690
you should know its condition very well.

659
00:37:14,530 --> 00:37:15,990
I said that because I believe

660
00:37:16,070 --> 00:37:17,130
you'll be able to make it.

661
00:37:17,550 --> 00:37:19,320
You've been in the mountains for decades.

662
00:37:19,500 --> 00:37:21,040
There's nothing you haven't seen.

663
00:37:24,080 --> 00:37:26,280
Sir, if you refuse to help,

664
00:37:26,360 --> 00:37:28,500
his friends might actually die
in the mountains.

665
00:37:36,890 --> 00:37:38,460
It's not that I don't want to help

666
00:37:39,630 --> 00:37:41,130
or I'm afraid of dying,

667
00:37:41,790 --> 00:37:44,300
but I won't let you die in vain.

668
00:37:45,630 --> 00:37:47,540
They're staying by the lake,

669
00:37:48,390 --> 00:37:49,400
not in the mountains,

670
00:37:49,480 --> 00:37:50,500
I guess

671
00:37:51,510 --> 00:37:52,850
they will be fine.

672
00:37:54,310 --> 00:37:55,650
Based on my experience,

673
00:37:56,250 --> 00:37:58,990
it should stop raining
in two or three days.

674
00:37:59,180 --> 00:38:01,860
I'll take you there then.

675
00:38:27,970 --> 00:38:29,440
Panma is a stubborn old man.

676
00:38:29,660 --> 00:38:31,210
We can definitely go in the mountains,

677
00:38:31,520 --> 00:38:33,710
it's just that the rain
makes it a little difficult to walk.

678
00:38:34,160 --> 00:38:35,250
He just wants to steer clear of trouble.

679
00:38:35,660 --> 00:38:38,250
Whenever it rains,
he'd go on and on about mudslides.

680
00:38:38,740 --> 00:38:40,370
Does mudslide happen so easily?

681
00:38:41,180 --> 00:38:43,890
I have only seen mudslide once
my whole life.

682
00:38:45,660 --> 00:38:46,560
I have another idea.

683
00:38:49,310 --> 00:38:50,180
What idea?

684
00:38:50,260 --> 00:38:51,160
Don't ask.

685
00:38:51,390 --> 00:38:53,280
Try to get me a set of old overalls.

686
00:38:53,630 --> 00:38:54,690
If it's possible,

687
00:38:55,390 --> 00:38:56,560
get me a female wig as well.
